<li>Sending you love and strength during this painful time.</li>
<li>Thinking of you and your family with heartfelt sorrow. May your memories bring you solace.</li>
<li>Words cannot express the sadness I feel upon hearing of your husband's passing.</li>
<li>He was such a kind and wonderful man.  My heart goes out to you all.</li>
<li>You are in my thoughts and prayers during this difficult time.</li>
<li>Please accept my sincere condolences on the loss of your beloved husband.</li>
<li>May the love you shared bring you comfort in the days ahead.</li>
<li>I am so very sorry for your loss.  He will be fondly remembered.</li>
<li>Holding you and your family close in my heart.</li>
<li>Your husband’s memory will live on through the love you shared.</li>
<li>Sending you strength and peace during this time of sorrow.</li>
<li>May happy memories bring you comfort during this difficult period.</li>
<li>Please let me know if there is anything I can do to help.</li>
<li>With deepest sympathy and heartfelt condolences.</li>
    

